Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,God is prompt, so we try to be prompt.\NIt's 9 o'clock, God's here, so it's good to see you all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Last week we were in Austin, so if you're from Austin and you're here today, say hello\Nto them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.61,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We start out, we have an interpreter here also.\NI can't hear what she's saying, but she knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The rate my hearing is going, I'll be needing her soon.\NSo I'm buttering her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.32,0:08:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I say what more than any other word in the language.\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.28,0:08:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NNow I have this African parrot that makes my what's even worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.34,0:08:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NShe said Merry Christmas this morning, so that's her message to the group.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been following the advance of her consciousness, you know, and she's learning all kinds of\Nlanguage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.72,0:08:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And now she says, ho, ho, ho, Merry Christmas.\NWhen Jesus returns, she'd be all ready for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.43,0:09:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So, as you know, we always start out with the end of the lecture first and work back\Nto the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The realization, there's only a few things you really need to know.\NThere's only a couple of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know just a few things.\NIf you know the things very well, that's all you need.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To merely hear them already begins the process.\NJust before the world disappears altogether, you notice that everything is happening spontaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.33,0:10:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The most important thing to know is that everything is happening in and of its own.\NNothing is being caused by anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.58,0:10:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All phenomena.\NAll phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.24,0:10:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All phenomena are the automatic consequence of the field.\NThe field is one of infinite, invisible, omnipotent power.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.33,0:10:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All encompassing.\NLike a giant electromagnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No beginning, no ending.\NEither spatially or in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Forever and always present.\NThis field is infinitely powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The human mind cannot conceive of the infinite.\NExcept as a concept.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.36,0:11:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Its presence is exquisitely gentle and exquisitely powerful.\NThe field is so powerful that potentiality is activated by the field to become an actuality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.21,0:11:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,All things happen by virtue of the infinite power of the field.\NWhat the world considers evolution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.84,0:11:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the witnessing of creation which is continuous.\NThe unmanifest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.14,0:11:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The unmanifest.\NBeyond the linear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.56,0:11:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Becomes manifest by divine providence.\NAs the totality of creation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.09,0:11:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And this happens effortlessly.\NWithin the field then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.75,0:12:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Potentiality is actualized by intention.\NTherefore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.89,0:12:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Each thing comes forth.\NManifesting its karmic inheritance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You might say its karma is its innate potential.\NAnd when conditions are appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.80,0:12:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then the potentiality becomes an actuality.\NIn and of itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,In and of itself.\NAs a consequence of the infinite power of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The field is so powerful that if you continuously hold the thought.\NIt will become a happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NOtherwise no one will become enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.39,0:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore.\NOne's intention is all powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,See the ego is very clever.\NAnd as the thing begins to.
